::: Maine fires two optic lasers at Arcangle, while Inferno and Rampage 
continue to try and destry the hull. :::

~~~~~~~~~

::: Hell Beast takes Vuloris and Termeniss to the Brig. They are put in two 
seperate cells with force feilds. Rat Trap, who they forgot about is also in 
the Brig :::

::: Gremlin ::: Well, I doubt you two are going to live through this. Pheniox 
and Black Aracnia have been taking your lab apart for the past hour. Your 
stasis pod is going to be broken down into scrap, so you can tell your little 
friend she wont be going home etier.

::: Jackle, holding his pistol ::: Yeah. I mean, who did you think you were 
pulling something like that? As for your TM3 driver....I think that will be 
destroyed.

::: Transanulas, passing though looked at them ::: Also, dont try to break 
out. I have placed an emmiter in the command consul that controls this Brig. 
It will force you to stay in robot form. Try to escape, and you wont get very 
far with the energon.

:: The spider leaves, laughing hysterically. Gremlin and Jackle continue to 
stand guard. :::
